"{\"uid\": \"nbcphiladelphia.com-paris-2024-summer-olympics-how-pole-vaulters-travel-with-poles-mondo-duplantis-3932438\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Mosttrack and fieldathletes could easily fit their uniforms and gear in a suitcase to travel to a competition like the2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 138, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 137, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But some have massive poles to worry about.\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 182, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ReigningOlympicpole vault championMondo Duplantisdetailed to NBC how he gets his 17-foot poles from one place to another.\", \"from\": 184, \"to\": 305, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 245, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9936445575077055, \"rank\": 0.0031214457049843474, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Here's a hint: it's not easy.)\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stream Philadelphia News for free, 24/7, wherever you are with NBC10.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia\", \"score\": 0.9987692528077514, \"rank\": 0.001213325532603984, \"text\": \"Philadelphia\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philadelphia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Swedish athlete and Lafayette, Louisiana, native said he first has to find flights that are able to store his bag of poles before paying for oversized luggage fees.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 414, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9980596596454557, \"rank\": 0.00154651748675062, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lafayette, Louisiana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\"}, {\"begin\": 434, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lafayette, Louisiana\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lafayette,_Louisiana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, Duplantis will draw some confused looks as he lugs the poles through the airport.\", \"from\": 579, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's very difficult to travel with them,\\\" Duplantis said.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I am in the airport, I am just yelling, 'excuse me!'\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"like the whole time...And everybody's just so confused.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 843, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They think it might be skis, but (the bag) is like 20-feet long.\", \"from\": 844, \"to\": 908, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the center of attention when I walk into an airport with the sticks.\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's for sure.\\\"\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1002, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Duplantis, 24, won gold in his Olympic debut at thepandemic-delayed 2020 Tokyo Games, beating out U.S. silver medalist Chris Nilsen.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1102, \"end\": 1122, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"U.S. silver medalist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/U.S._Figure_Skating_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1123, \"end\": 1135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Nilsen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chris Nilsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Nilsen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chris_Nilsen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he will surely be hoping to pick up another gold in Paris before having to begin the trek back home with his poles.\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1256, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995557118, \"rank\": 4.4436660319043344e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's pole vault competition at the Paris Games begins with thequalification roundonSaturday, Aug. 3 at 4:10 a.m.\", \"from\": 1258, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1379, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch men's pole vault qualification live on Aug. 3 at 4:10 a.m.\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET  The men's pole vault final will follow on Monday, Aug. 5 at 1 p.m.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the women's side, qualification is set for Aug. 5 at 4:40 a.m.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1587, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET followed by the final on Wednesday, Aug. 7 at 1 p.m.\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Stade de France in Saint-Denis, France, is the site of the Olympictrack and field events.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1649, \"end\": 1664, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1668, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 0.9999423967394563, \"rank\": 5.759324670797031e-05, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1681, \"end\": 1687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8730489070624368, \"rank\": 0.12443966095486528, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Duplantis broke his own men's world record at a Diamond League event in Xiamen, China, this past April when he cleared 6.24 meters (20 feet, 5 inches), topping his previous mark of 6.23 meters.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999985586051864, \"rank\": 1.3226021142310489e-06, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.o